The three individuals are making their way towards a cave, the mouth
of which is just large enough for the humans to enter. The mouth is
covered in dead vines and strange brownish green foliage that looks
vaguely unnatural.

After a brief look around they each enter the cave mouth one at a
time, the one with the wheelbarrel is able to wedge it through the
opening, but just barely.

(TAG)

- Preston
